description: Redevelopment to provide a mixed use scheme in 2no. buildings (a 3 storey block fronting Pier Road and a 16 storey block positioned further into the site), comprising 97no. residential units of 1, 2 and 3 bedrooms (including 31no. Key worker units), a cafe (A3 use, 111sq.m) for the public, and a gym for members and non members (295 sq.m); including landscaping works and ancillary car (40 spaces), motorcycle (13 spaces) and bicycle (42 spaces) parking (revised plans).
